&lt;p&gt;Very simple ! Here is my suggestion : &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you want to select dataframes in your workspace, try this :&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-r s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-r&quot;&gt;Filter&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; is.data.frame&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;get&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; ls&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;or &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-r s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-r&quot;&gt;ls&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;sapply&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;ls&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; is.data.frame&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;get&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;all these will give the same result. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can change &lt;code&gt;is.data.frame&lt;/code&gt; to check other types of variables like &lt;code&gt;is.function&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the tidyverse, you can use the function &lt;code&gt;lst()&lt;/code&gt; to automatically name the lists based on the objects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-r s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-r&quot;&gt;library&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;tibble&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

d1 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; data.frame&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;y1 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-built_in&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
                 y2 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-built_in&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
d2 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; data.frame&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;y1 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-built_in&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
                 y2 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-built_in&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

lst&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;d1&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; d2&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot;&gt;# $d1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot;&gt;# y1 y2&lt;/span&gt;
